# Using

To use FileExchange you need to install the [.NET Core 3.1](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download/dotnet/3.1) package.
Then you need edit your config file "appsettings.json".

## Configuration
### Database("Db" -> "Connect")
[Template]: "Data Source=[HOTS];Initial Catalog=[DB_NAME];Persist Security Info=True;User ID=[USER_NAME];Password=[USER_PASSWORD]"

### FTP("FTP")
"EnableSFTP" - Enable or Disable SFTP (default: False)

"Username" - Username in FTP server

"Password" - Password in FTP server

"Host" - FTP server host

"Port" - FTP server port

"RootPath" - Working folder on FTP server